<R extends RelNode> SolrConverterRule(Class<R> clazz, Predicate<RelNode> predicate, String description) {
      super(clazz, predicate::test, Convention.NONE, SolrRel.CONVENTION, description);
      this.out = SolrRel.CONVENTION;
    }
